page.title: 16Forestry in our area
page.content: There are three main forests in the area Birks,Rainsbarrow and new plantation.These are some of the trees in the woods, scotchpine,oak,spindle(shrub),ash, alder buckthorn(shrub)sycamore,hazel (shrub),beech,willow,alder,crab apple, birch,hawthorn(shrub),mountain ash,holly,cherry,hornbeam,whitebeam, larch and hemlock. There are five forestry workers who live in forestry houses.They fell trees and pull them out of the wood with a tractor. The wood goes to Workington. Contractors come from all over the country to take it away.
